---
// CTA.astro
---

<section class="py-24 px-5">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-coral/20 via-brand-card to-brand-card border border-brand-coral/30 rounded-[2.5rem] p-12 md:p-16 text-center">

      <!-- Glow -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-hero-glow opacity-60 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <!-- Decorative circles -->
      <div class="absolute -top-16 -right-16 w-48 h-48 rounded-full bg-brand-coral/10 blur-3xl pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-16 -left-16 w-64 h-64 rounded-full bg-brand-coral/5 blur-3xl pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="inline-block text-5xl mb-6">🚀</div>
        <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-white mb-5 leading-tight">
          ¿Listo para que tu Airbnb<br />trabaje por ti, estés donde estés?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-muted text-xl mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Empieza hoy con un análisis gratuito de ingresos.
          Sin compromiso. Resultados visibles en 30 días.
        </p>

        <a
          href="/empezar/"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-brand-coral hover:bg-orange-500 text-white font-bold text-lg px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(255,84,54,0.5)] hover:-translate-y-1 active:scale-95"
        >
          <span>EMPEZAR AHORA — GRATIS</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/>
          </svg>
        </a>

        <p class="mt-6 text-brand-muted text-sm flex items-center justify-center gap-4 flex-wrap">
          <span>🔒 Sin permanencia</span>
          <span>✅ Garantía 30 días</span>
          <span>💳 Sin tarjeta de crédito</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
